column5: I think most views are from guys trying to find out what brand of marshmellow works best in the spring... keep yer mouth closed Dann, don't be giving away our secrets! HH
46000 crushed gobie hits and counting.
60,011,612  Thats what it says on the botom of the page.It came and went in silence, without pomp and cerimony
We reached it last night at 11:40...I'm verklempt.

Back on December 12th 2010 I predicted that our new board would hit 60,000,000 views around mid March 2011. Well folks, it appears that we'll hit that number in two and a half days. Seeing as March has 31 days, that's about as mid March as you can get. I feel so gifted.  Thanks everyone for being a part of this great community of ours and contributing as much as you all have.
March is long gone.... This is April.....
